le":"symbol","roleHeading":"Class","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"class","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView.h#L14","fileName":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView.h"}},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView/userLocation":{"role":"symbol"